# Scenario analysis

## Implied shocks

$$
\begin{aligned}
\hat{\beta}&=(Z^\mathrm{T}WZ)^{-1}Z^\mathrm{T}WX
\end{aligned}
$$


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
implied_shocks <- function(shocks, x, z, weights) {

    beta <- solve(crossprod(z, diag(weights) %*% z)) %*% crossprod(z, diag(weights) %*% x)

    result <- shocks %*% beta

    return(result)

}
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
shocks <- c(-0.1, 0.1)
overlap_z_xts <- overlap_x_xts[ , 1:2]
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
